- **ğŸ“ Comprehensive Logging**: Detailed logs for troubleshooting

### ğŸ”’ **Security & Reliability**
- **ğŸ›¡ï¸ Secure Password Input**: Hidden password entry (never stored/logged)
- **ğŸ§¹ Session Cleanup**: Automatic browser data cleanup after use
